os Module (MOST IMPORTANT)
os kya hai?


os.getcwd()


Kaam:

current working directory batata hai

Use case:

script kis folder mein run ho rahi hai

üîπ os.listdir()
os.listdir()


Kaam:

current folder ke saare files & folders ki list deta hai

Return type:

list

Example output:

['day1.py', 'test.txt', 'image.jpg']

